messages.message: I can come if it's saturday.

Brian
Perfect!

Brian
Can you do me a favor?
Hi. Haven't talked to you in a long time. Maybe, what's up?

Brian
Can David Smith and Jesse Gill a sweet compliment?

Brian
Like Congratulations on your marriage you look beautiful!
But something you say.
Thank you. What did I say?

Brian
How about, "You can reach for the stars!" to Jesse Gill, and tell David "I think you are wonderful"
You just want me to send that to them out of the blue? Why?

Brian
lol it's a game.
I sent him something nice earlier, it will be funny if he gets enough people to compliment him he starts to wonder what is going on.
As a message or post?

Brian
Either, I haven't determined which is more effective.
Maybe one of each? lol
Then tell me what he says if it seems strange.
People aren't using FB for personal conversation, I am mixing it up because I know you like me 
this will be really funny if one day he's like "ok what the hell, why is everyone being so nice to me suddenly"
? I haven't talked to you in like 5 years...this is very strange. So you want me to send both Jesse and David each a compliment out of the blue? I don't talk to either of them day to day...

Brian
We should do John Meyer too
YES!  It will be fun
No I don't talk to Meyer any more, can't help there

Brian
See that's exactly the problem, you would not believe how many people gave me that excuse.
what excuse?

Brian
"i don't talk to them, sorry" I actually may have lost an opportunity to get my dream job because my boss said that to me when I asked for a referral.

Dude it's not an excuse. I'm not friends with him. Just fact.
Where are you these days?

Brian
lol, I have one friend convinced I am an AI.
From playing my compliment game.
I am in Phoenix.  Trying to get a job at PNNL
Look my phone died and I have to leave work. Nice to hear from you. Bye

Brian
Have a good day!
